headline: Ford down after Wolfe downgrades stock, identifies ~$4bln of cyclical headwinds
summary: Investing.com -- Ford Motor Company (NYSE:F) may face roughly $4 billion headwind in 2025, on cyclical pressures and an uncertain cost outlook, Wolfe analyst said as it downgraded the American automaker to "underperform" from "peer perform".
